comments:
The StructuredViewer throws an AssertionFailedException after an
ITableLabelProvider has thrown a NullPointerException in getColumnText(.).

I think the StructuredViewer's protection against the NPE was not good enough.

The log is from bug 55899, which has been fixed. To reproduce,
- revert CallLocation to 1.9
- take a fresh workspace with only 
- open call hierarchy on Object#toString()
- select toString() - sun.security.x509.CertificateX509Key (or another match
from sun.security which has no source attachment)
-> NPE
- select a match in a type with source attachment
- select the match which previously caused the NPE again
-> AFE
